body:
When you enter a New World for the first time, you will receive a new item called the Starter Orb. With this item, you can choose a starter kit of items to start your journey. All items follow the class name line, in addition to one or more potion effects for the next 5 minutes of kit selection. In the future, we will update the Orb GUI to make it more charismatic, but for now, enjoy and discover all the classes/kits and their specialties.



List of current kits:

- Swordsman;

- Lumberjack;

- Miner;

- Farmer;

- The Mole;

- Fisherman;

- Archer;

- Bomberman;

- Mage;

- Beast Tamer.
